ol.li:
Create a data file containing the payload for your certificate authentication
            settings. For example, cb-certauth-setting.json:
            {
	"state": "enable",
	"prefixes": [{
			"path": "san.uri",
			"prefix": "www.",
			"delimiter": "."
		},
		{
			"path": "san.email",
			"prefix": "couchbase.",
			"delimiter": "."
		}
	]
}
